{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"About a year ago,"},{"time":4000,"text":"I asked myself a question:"},{"time":6000,"text":"\"Knowing what I know,"},{"time":8000,"text":"why am I not a vegetarian?\""},{"time":10000,"text":"After all, I'm one of the green guys:"},{"time":13000,"text":"I grew up with hippie parents in a log cabin."},{"time":16000,"text":"I started a site called TreeHugger --"},{"time":21000,"text":"I care about this stuff."},{"time":24000,"text":"I knew that eating a mere hamburger a day"},{"time":26000,"text":"can increase my risk of dying by a third."},{"time":30000,"text":"Cruelty: I knew that the 10 billion"},{"time":33000,"text":"animals we raise each year for meat"},{"time":36000,"text":"are raised in factory farm conditions"},{"time":39000,"text":"that we, hypocritically, wouldn't even consider"},{"time":42000,"text":"for our own cats, dogs and other pets."},{"time":46000,"text":"Environmentally, meat, amazingly,"},{"time":49000,"text":"causes more emissions"},{"time":51000,"text":"than all of transportation combined:"},{"time":53000,"text":"cars, trains, planes, buses, boats, all of it."},{"time":57000,"text":"And beef production uses 100 times the water"},{"time":60000,"text":"that most vegetables do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"I also knew that I'm not alone."},{"time":68000,"text":"We as a society"},{"time":70000,"text":"are eating twice as much meat"},{"time":72000,"text":"as we did in the 50s."},{"time":75000,"text":"So what was once the special little side treat"},{"time":78000,"text":"now is the main, much more regular."},{"time":80000,"text":"So really, any of these angles"},{"time":82000,"text":"should have been enough to convince me to go vegetarian."},{"time":85000,"text":"Yet, there I was -- chk, chk, chk --"},{"time":87000,"text":"tucking into a big old steak."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"So why was I stalling?"},{"time":93000,"text":"I realized that what I was being pitched"},{"time":95000,"text":"was a binary solution."},{"time":97000,"text":"It was either"},{"time":99000,"text":"you're a meat eater or you're a vegetarian,"},{"time":102000,"text":"and I guess I just wasn't quite ready."},{"time":105000,"text":"Imagine your last hamburger."},{"time":108000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":112000,"text":"So my common sense,"},{"time":115000,"text":"my good intentions,"},{"time":118000,"text":"were in conflict with my taste buds."},{"time":120000,"text":"And I'd commit to doing it later,"},{"time":123000,"text":"and not surprisingly, later never came."},{"time":126000,"text":"Sound familiar?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":129000,"text":"So I wondered,"},{"time":131000,"text":"might there be a third solution?"},{"time":134000,"text":"And I thought about it, and I came up with one."},{"time":136000,"text":"I've been doing it for the last year, and it's great."},{"time":139000,"text":"It's called weekday veg."},{"time":142000,"text":"The name says it all:"},{"time":144000,"text":"Nothing with a face Monday through Friday."},{"time":146000,"text":"On the weekend, your choice."},{"time":150000,"text":"Simple."},{"time":152000,"text":"If you want to take it to the next level,"},{"time":154000,"text":"remember, the major culprits"},{"time":156000,"text":"in terms of environmental damage and health"},{"time":159000,"text":"are red and processed meats."},{"time":161000,"text":"So you want to swap those out"},{"time":163000,"text":"with some good, sustainably harvested fish."},{"time":166000,"text":"It's structured,"},{"time":168000,"text":"so it ends up being simple to remember,"},{"time":170000,"text":"and it's okay to break it here and there."},{"time":173000,"text":"After all, cutting five days a week"},{"time":175000,"text":"is cutting 70 percent of your meat intake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178000,"text":"The program has been great, weekday veg."},{"time":181000,"text":"My footprint's smaller,"},{"time":183000,"text":"I'm lessening pollution,"},{"time":185000,"text":"I feel better about the animals,"},{"time":187000,"text":"I'm even saving money."},{"time":189000,"text":"Best of all, I'm healthier,"},{"time":191000,"text":"I know that I'm going to live longer,"},{"time":194000,"text":"and I've even lost a little weight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"So, please ask yourselves,"},{"time":200000,"text":"for your health,"},{"time":202000,"text":"for your pocketbook,"},{"time":204000,"text":"for the environment, for the animals:"},{"time":207000,"text":"What's stopping you from giving weekday veg a shot?"},{"time":210000,"text":"After all, if all of us"},{"time":213000,"text":"ate half as much meat,"},{"time":215000,"text":"it would be like half of us"},{"time":217000,"text":"were vegetarians."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}